Package: NeAtlIBTS64
Title: Scripts and functions for the IBTSNeAtl in 64bits 
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Francisco", "Velasco", , "Franvgls@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-6420-9474"))
Description: R 4.x port of NeAtlIBTS. Provides quality-control plotting and
    DATRAS-based analysis functions for ICES International Bottom Trawl
    Surveys in the Northeast Atlantic. Includes gear-parameter plots
    (door spread, wing spread, warp length, net opening), haul-level QC
    (distance, speed, course, position), survey map wrappers, and helpers
    for handling historical and ongoing bottom-trawl survey data.
